e%20Church%20offers%20to%20everyone%20the%20treasury%20of%20her%20social%20teaching%20in%20response%20to%20another%20industrial%20revolution%20and%20to%20developments%20in%20the%20field%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20that%20pose%20new%20challenges%20for%20the%20defence%20of%20human%20dignity%2C%20justice%20and%20labor%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20first%20US-born%20pope%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPitigoi-Aron%20said%20church%20leaders%20who%20leverage%20technology%20don't%20want%20to%20replace%20people%20or%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehuman%20aspects%20of%20worship.%20Rather%2C%20it's%20meant%20to%20amplify%20their%20mission%20and%20create%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELivestreaming%20also%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20popular%20tech%20tool%20for%20church%20leaders%20during%20and%20after%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20Nearly%2090%25%20of%20surveyed%20church%20leaders%20said%20they%20live-streamed%20worship%20services%20or%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPaul%20the%20Apostle%20took%20ships%20from%20place%20to%20place%20and%20told%20people%20about%20Jesus%2C%20right%3F%20Now%20you're%20livestreaming%2C%26quot%3B%20Pitigoi-Aron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETechnology%20has%20also%20influenced%20how%20the%20church%20navigates%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnline%20giving%20continues%20to%20be%20the%20most%20popular%20digital%20solution%20among%20all%20churches%20%E2%80%94%20not%20surprising%2C%20considering%2070%25%20of%20leaders%20believe%20technology%20has%20increased%20generosity%20in%20their%20church.%20That%20proven%20impact%20is%20likely%20responsible%20for%20the%20fast-growing%20interest%20in%20accepting%20cryptocurrency%20and%20stock%20donations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%2010%25%20of%20surveyed%20church%20leaders%20said%20they're%20leveraging%20cryptocurrency%2C%20but%2039%25%20said%20it%20will%20become%20%26quot%3Bstrategically%20important%20to%20their%20church%20in%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20years.%26quot%3B%20That's%20a%2044%25%20increase%20from%202024%2C%20but%2062%25%20of%20respondents%20said%20they%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20know%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bneed%20to%20learn%20more%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPitigoi-Aron%20said%20non-traditional%20giving%2C%20like%20stocks%20and%20cryptocurrency%2C%20could%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20opportunity%26quot%3B%20for%20churches.%20In%20the%20digital%20age%2C%20where%20nearly%20everything%20is%20one%20click%20away%2C%20accepting%20new%20platforms%20can%20lower%20the%20barrier%20of%20entry%20for%20some%20congregants%20hoping%20to%20donate%20and%20connect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20some%20church%20leaders%20are%20now%20using%20QR%20codes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTangentially%2C%20QR%20codes%20are%20being%20utilized%20more%20than%20ever%2C%20often%20to%20drive%20community%20members%20and%20streaming%20viewers%20to%20next%20steps%20via%20a%20simple%20scan%20or%20tap%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20increasing%20focus%20on%20modern%20technology%20isn't%20just%20talk%20for%20church%20leaders.%20Over%20half%20said%20they%20increased%20their%20tech%20budgets%20over%20the%20last%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchurch-technology-ai-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748166001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68322bcac6ad288d1481dd72%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchurch-technology-ai-cryptocurrency-bitcoin-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%202025%20State%20of%20the%20Church%20Tech%20report%20said%2045%25%20of%20surveyed%20church%20leaders%20now%20use%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20an%2080%25%20jump%20from%20last%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ledmonds%40businessinsider.com%20(Lauren%20Edmonds)%22%2C%22eng