Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPhysical%20therapy%20company%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestors-executives-got-rich-hinge-health-ipo-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHinge%20Health%20went%20public%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20week%20in%20a%20blockbuster%20move%20for%20the%20digital%20health%20market.%20Now%2C%20as%20a%20public%20company%2C%20Hinge%20Health%20is%20planning%20to%20keep%20investing%20heavily%20in%20AI%20to%20automate%20care%20delivery%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20first%20healthcare%20delivery%20startup%20to%20IPO%20in%20years%20%E2%80%94%20and%20for%20the%20first%20mover%2C%20it's%20setting%20a%20strong%20example.%20In%20the%20first%20quarter%20of%20the%20year%2C%20Hinge%20Health%20recorded%20an%2081%25%20gross%20margin%20and%20brought%20in%20%24123.8%20million%20in%20revenue%20with%20a%20%2417.1%20million%20profit%2C%20giving%20investors%20the%20high%20margins%20and%20the%20profitability%20they've%20long%20sought%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstakes-for-healthcare-ipo-are-higher-than-ever-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20IPOs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Daniel%20Perez%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20startup%20has%20been%20able%20to%20hit%20those%20financials%2C%20in%20part%2C%20by%20using%20AI%20to%20help%20slash%2095%25%20of%20clinician%20hours%20spent%20on%20PT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20long-term%20vision%20is%20to%20continue%20to%20peel%20away%20aspects%20of%20in-person%20care%20and%20deliver%20the%20care%20itself%20via%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20Perez%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20Thursday%20morning%2C%20before%20Hinge%20Health's%20stock%20began%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerez%20cofounded%20Hinge%20Health%20with%20Gabriel%20Mecklenburg%20in%202014%20to%20provide%20virtual%20care%20for%20musculoskeletal%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20joint%20and%20back%20pain.%20The%20startup%20provides%20personalized%20care%20plans%2C%20exercise%20therapy%2C%20messaging%20with%20clinicians%2C%20and%20wearable%20pain-relief%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20already%20leveraging%20AI%20for%20care%20coordination%20and%20motion%20tracking%2C%20using%20AI-powered%20computer%20vision%20to%20track%20patient%20movements%20during%20exercises%20and%20adjust%20their%20treatment%20plans%20based%20on%20the%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20is%20also%20planning%20to%20expand%20outside%20physical%20therapy%20into%20new%20care%20areas%2C%20Perez%20said.%20While%20he%20didn't%20name%20what%20specialties%20Hinge%20Health%20will%20target%20next%2C%20he%20said%20the%20company%20anticipates%20making%20announcements%20this%20summer%20about%20its%20efforts%20to%20dig%20deeper%20into%20musculoskeletal%20care%2C%20as%20well%20as%20releases%20in%202026%20that%20enable%20Hinge%20Health%20to%20deliver%20care%20in%20specialties%20adjacent%20to%20physical%20therapy%2C%20elevated%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20some%20point%2C%20whether%2010%2C%2050%2C%20or%20200%20years%20in%20the%20future%2C%20care%20delivery%20will%20be%20automated%20with%20technology.%20And%20that's%20a%20good%20thing%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff9c0e67-6839-4d11-8839-8f3941e3382d%5C%22%3EAutomation%20in%20volatile%20markets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHinge%20Health%20began%20trading%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange%20Thursday%20with%20the%20ticker%20%26quot%3BHNGE%26quot%3B%20at%20an%20initial%20share%20price%20of%20%2432%2C%20at%20the%20top%20end%20of%20its%20expected%20range%2C%20at%20a%20%242.6%20billion%20valuation.%20Its%20shares%20popped%20at%20its%20public%20market%20debut%2C%20jumping%20to%20%2439.25%20a%20share%2C%2023%25%20up%20from%20its%20initial%20pricing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20was%20forced%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhinge-health-delaying-planned-ipo-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Econsider%20delaying%20its%20IPO%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April%20after%20President%