%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20ready%20for%20that.%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-employee-engagement-workplace-morale-careers-boomers-gen-x-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecouldn't%20grasp%20living%20the%209-to-5%20lifestyle%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20a%20cousin%20who%20lived%20on%20Nantucket%2C%20and%20he%20told%20me%20to%20check%20it%20out.%20I%20did%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnanny-nantucket-nashville-toddler-wealthy-family-private-jet-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20summer%20of%20my%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20worked%20at%20a%20restaurant%20with%20a%20bunch%20of%20people%20from%20Croatia%20and%20became%20super%20good%20friends%20with%20them.%20I%20visited%20them%20in%20Croatia%20for%20what%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%2010%20days%2C%20and%20ended%20up%20traveling%20through%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20for%20the%20next%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E10%20months%20of%20that%20time%2C%20I%20owned%20a%20little%20market%20in%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20and%20my%20market%20relied%20on%20the%20tuk-tuks%20to%20bring%20customers%20to%20us.%20I'd%20already%20thought%20pedicabs%20would%20be%20a%20fun%20idea%20after%20going%20to%20school%20in%20Charleston%2C%20where%20they're%20popular.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20that%20they%20would%20work%20in%20Nantucket%20%E2%80%94%20and%20I%20figured%20that'd%20be%20a%20good%20way%20to%20keep%20the%20Peter%20Pan%20plan%20going%20a%20little%20longer%20and%20push%20off%20growing%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221587e86b-4f9f-4ddb-8935-aa0930ddd778%5C%22%3EThe%20summer%20I%20started%20NanTukTuk%20was%20the%20worst%20of%20my%20life%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENantucket%20is%20a%20traditional%20New%20England%20town%2C%20and%20people%20were%20not%20open%20to%20a%20new%20business.%20It%20took%20about%2010%20months%20and%20a%20dozen%20advisory%20committee%20hearings%20to%20get%20approval%20for%20the%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20I%20got%20approval%20in%20July%2C%20I%20started%20the%20business%2C%20and%20it%20was%20the%20worst%20summer%20of%20my%20life.%20Everything%20was%20barely%20working%20out.%20I%20was%20so%20close%20to%20just%20collapsing%2C%20and%20I%20perpetually%20felt%20like%20I%20was%20on%20the%20brink%20of%20disaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20bought%20two%20pedicabs%20at%20about%20%243%2C500%20each%2C%20which%20was%20a%20devastating%20blow%20for%20me%20at%20the%20time.%20I%20had%20a%20great%20first%20few%20days%20of%20business%2C%20but%20then%20the%20novelty%20wore%20off%20and%20people%20stopped%20giving%20me%20money.%20The%20town%20prohibited%20me%20from%20charging%20rides%20the%20first%20season%2C%20so%20people%20could%20only%20give%20me%20gratuity%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20handful%20of%20people%20who%20just%20weren't%20paying%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20thought%20I%20could%20figure%20out%20housing%2C%20but%20it's%20like%20%246%2C000%20to%20rent%20a%20comfortable%20spot%20here.%20So%20I%20spent%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20living%20out%20of%20the%20bed%20of%20my%20truck%20in%20a%20remote%20beach%20parking%20lot%20because%20it's%20illegal%20to%20camp%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michael%20Gormley%20pickup%20truck%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68307a3e6ffb6822ec6154ae%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20spent%20the%20first%20few%20weeks%20living%20out%20of%20the%20bed%20of%20my%20truck.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Gormley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20miserable.%20I%20would%20be%20up%20until%202%3A00%20a.m.%20working%20and%20then%20the%20sun%20would%20rise%20early%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20and%20I%20would%20be%20in%20the%20bed%20of%20my%20truck%20with%20the%20black%20tarp%20that%20rolls%20over%20the%20bed.%20It%20was%20so%20hot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20making%20enough%2C%20but%20not%20that%20much%2C%20and%20I%20was%20like%2C%20all%20right%2C%20maybe%20a%209-to-5%20isn't%20such%20a%20bad%20idea%20after%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c0547eb-6abb-46a1-9606-bb5037d24cf5%5C%22%3EThe%20business%20started%20to%20turn%20around%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F23-year-old-seasonal-worker-nantucket-aspen-money-perks-job-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EThe%20next%20season%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20we%20ended%20up%20getting%20two%20more%20tuk-tuks%20and%20hired%20three%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnantucket-homes-give-away-free-move-houses-cost-reason-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20ended%20up%20meeting%20people%20who%20helped%20me%20out%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20gave%20me%20close%20to%20free%20and%20discounted%20housing%20for%20periods%20of%20time%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlue%20Flag%20Capital%2C%20a%20private%20equity%20firm%2C%20helped%20me%20store%20the%20tuk%20tuks%20and%20fed%20me%20business%20through%20their%20hotel%20and%20restaurant%20guests.%20If%20it%20weren't%20for%20them%2C%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I%20would%20have%20made%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20created%20a%20spreadsheet%20of%20every%20wedding%20planner%20and%20venue%20on%20Nantucket%20and%20contacted%20all%20of%20them.%20I%20also%20gave%20a%20flyer%20and%20pamphlet%20to%20every%20hotel%20concierge%20and%20put%20door%20hangers%20on%20every%20house%20in%20the%20wealthiest%20neighborhood%20of%20Nantucket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222336%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michael%20Gormley%20riding%20NanTukTuk%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6830c8c66ffb6822ec6165b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221752%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIt%20took%20time%2C%20accountability%2C%20and%20credibility%20to%20prove%20to%20everyone%20we%20weren't%20scamming.%3Cp%3EBrittany%20Daniel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20time%20and%20credibility%20to%20prove%20to%20everyone%20that%20we%20weren't%20scamming%20them%20%E2%80%94%20and%20a%20handful%20of%20influential%20people%20in%20the%20community%20to%20start%20posting%20and%20talking%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-mistakes-tourists-make-in-times-square-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City%2C%20it%20gets%20confusing%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20customers%20because%20there%20are%20different%20rates%20per%20person%20or%20per%20block.%20I%20always%20confirm%20the%20final%20price%20with%20the%20rider%20before%20they%20get%20on.%20I%20tell%20my%20employees%20to%20charge%20in%20the%20%2410%20to%20%2450%20range%20and%20be%20very%20upfront%20with%20the%20cost%20so%20that%20no%20one%20is%20offended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20I'm%20signing%20more%20contracts.%20Some%20are%20worth%20%24100%20and%20others%20are%20worth%20thousands.%20I%20made%20%2410%2C000%20off%20an%20advertising%20contract%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20usually%20make%20about%20%241%2C000%20for%20events%2C%20but%20I%20have%20a%20good%20amount%20of%20events%20priced%20between%20%242%2C500%20and%20%244%2C000.%20It%20depends%20on%20how%20many%20tuk-tuks%20are%20booked%20and%20for%20how%20many%20hours.%20Ideally%2C%20people%20book%20out%20all%20four.%20We%20can%20only%20fit%20two%20to%20three%20people%20in%20the%20tuk-tuk%2C%20and%20we%20have%20a%20specific%20zone%20that%20we%20can%20operate%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20weddings%20or%20other%20events%2C%20tuk-tuks%20ride%20the%20couple%20around%20the%20town%20and%20deliver%20people%20to%20the%20main%20venue.%20It's%20useful%20for%20people%20with%20mobility%20impairments%20or%20women%20wearing%20heels.%20We%20also%20work%20with%20hotels%20and%20restaurants%20to%20provide%20transportation%20to%20guests.%20Kids%20love%20riding%20in%20the%20tuk-tuks%2C%20and%20sometimes%2C%20parents%20will%20pay%20us%20to%20take%20them%20on%20loops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22726%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Michael%20Gormley%20riding%20NanTukTuk%20at%20wedding%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6830f4c36ffb6822ec616d29%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221068%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20use%20a%20faux%20white%20flower%20wreath%20and%20get%20a%20bunch%20of%20Cisco%20brewery%20cans%20and%20tie%20them%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20tuck%20tuck.%20It's%20a%20fun%20photo%20opportunity%20and%20such%20a%20blast.%3Cp%3EMichael%20Gormley%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2285ad930a-f59c-43f7-8996-5ab4027a4eab%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20plan%20on%20doing%20it%20forever%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20love%20collaborating%20with%20other%20small%20businesses.%20I%20also%20don't%20need%20to%20get%20approval%20for%20anything%20from%20a%20boss%2C%20and%20I%20never%20get%20tired%20of%20it.%20It's%20just%20intoxicating.%20There's%20always%20the%20thought%20of%20how%20else%20I%20can%20get%20revenue%20streaming.%20Or%2C%20what%20can%20we%20change%20about%20this%20to%20make%20it%20better%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20long%20term%2C%20there's%20only%20so%20much%20money%20that%20can%20be%20made%20from%20it.%20I%20also%20work%20seven%20days%20a%20week%2C%20and%20it%20consumes%20me.%20I%20joke%20that%20I%20don't%20have%20a%20boss%2C%20but%20I%20have%20no%20freedom.%20I%20don't%20mind%20that%2C%20but%20in%20the%20long%20term%2C%20I%20want%20to%20do%20it%20for%20something%20with%20higher%20potential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20after%20one%20or%20two%20more%20seasons%2C%20it%20will%20have%20served%20its%20purpose%2C%20where%20I've%20learned%20a%20ton%2C%20worked%20a%20ton%2C%20and%20it%20could%20help%20inform%20me%20on%20my%20next%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20NanTukTuk%20allowed%20me%20to%20network%20tremendously%20and%20avoid%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20and%20I'm%20forever%20in%20debt%20to%20it%20for%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-started-pedicab-business-nantucket-to-avoid-corporate-job-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748162282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6830c8f8ca50259add4cf422%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-started-pedicab-business-nantucket-to-avoid-corporate-job-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sometimes%20I%20envy%20my%20pals%20who%20have%20weekends%2C%20but%20NanTukTuk%20has%20taught%20me%20so%20much%2C%20and%20it's%20allowed%20me%20to%20live%20in%20the%20most%20special%20place.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-started-pedicab-business-nantucket-to-avoid-corporate-job-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20Officials%20Airdrop%20Supplies%20To%20Farmers%20Stranded%20In%20Floods%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Recovery%20is%20under%20way%20in%20the%20mid-north%20coast%20region%20of%20Australia's%20most%20populous%20state%20after%20days%20of%20flooding%20cut%20off%20towns%2C%20swept%20away%20livestock%20and%20destroyed%20homes.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748162195000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-05%2Fre736mpg_australia_625x300_25_May_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Faustralian-officials-airdrop-supplies-to-farmers-stranded-in-floods-8502786%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recovery%20is%20under%20way%20in%20the%20mid-north%20coast%20region%20of%20Australia's%20most%20populous%20state%20after%20days%20of%20flooding%20cut%20off%20towns%2C%20swept%20away%20livestock%20and%20destroyed%20homes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22