ttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-data-centers-us-power-grid-gpu-nvidia-cerebras-amazon-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20power-hungry%20data%20centers%3C%2Fa%3E%20behind%20the%20technology%20%E2%80%94%20have%20put%20nuclear%20energy%20back%20on%20the%20map%20in%20just%20the%20past%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmicrosoft-plan-to-use-nuclear-energy-power-ai-data-centers-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-nuclear-power-strategy-ai-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20fueling%20the%20AI%20demand%2C%20are%20investing%20in%20newer%20reactor%20designs%20such%20as%20small%20modular%20reactors%20(SMRs)%2C%20driving%20what%20BI%20has%20called%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-nuclear-startups-ai-data-center-vc-boom-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20nuclear%20renaissance%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20four%20SMR%20companies%2C%20for%20example%2C%20have%20received%20nearly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmall-modular-reactor-venture-capital-ai-data-centers-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%243%20billion%20in%20equity%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BI%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20only%20AI%20that's%20driving%20the%20need%20for%20a%20reliable%20and%20constant%20source%20of%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPiercy%2C%20the%20American%20Nuclear%20Society%20CEO%2C%20said%20the%20US's%20push%20toward%20electrification%20and%20domestic%20manufacturing%2C%20which%20has%20been%20a%20top%20priority%20for%20the%20second%20Trump%20administration%2C%20will%20also%20significantly%20increase%20energy%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20the%20last%2020%20years%20or%20so%2C%20US%20electricity%20demand%20has%20essentially%20been