ould%20be%20assigned%20to%20a%20computer%20and%20help%20nuclear%20plants%20run%20more%20efficiently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20example%2C%20just%20monitoring%20if%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethere's%20anything%20going%20wrong.%20People%2C%20humans%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Vilim%20said.%20%26quot%3BNow%20you%20can%20assign%20that%20to%20an%20algorithm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20automation%20tool%20Vilim%20works%20with%20is%20PRO-AID%2C%20or%20Parameter-Free%20Reasoning%20Operator%20for%20Automated%20Identification%20and%20Diagnosis.%20It%20can%20be%20thought%20of%20as%20a%20digital%20assistant%20for%20monitoring%20and%20diagnosing%20reactors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVilim%20said%20the%20earliest%20iterations%20of%20PRO-AID%20were%20developed%20around%20the%20late%201990s.%20But%20over%20the%20next%20few%20decades%2C%20and%20with%20the%20arrival%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-chat-gpt-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EChatGPT%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%2C%20PRO-AID%20has%20been%20updated%20with%20a%20few%20new%20tricks%2C%20including%20reasoning%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVilim%20said%20that%20before%202022%2C%20PRO-AID%20would%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20an%20operator%20or%20system%20engineer%20whether%20there%20was%20a%20leak%20or%20if%20a%20particular%20component%20went%20offline.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20operators%20can%20do%20now%20is%20ask%20PRO-AID%3A%20Why%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20we're%20now%20using%20ChatGPT-type%20algorithms%20to%20go%20into%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20the%20model%2C%20examine%20the%20logic%20that%20led%20to%20the%20diagnosis%2C%20and%20compose%20an%20answer%20into%20human-understandable%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20Vilim%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20not%20only%20does%20the%20operator%20learn%2C%20'Oh%2C%20there's%20a%20leak%20outside%20containment%2C'%20he%20or%20she%20can%20query%20the%20system%20and%20say%2C%20'Well%2C%20why%20do%20you%20say%20that%3F'%26quot%3B