C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20but%20not%20both.%20And%20paying%20for%20daycare%20was%20out%20of%20the%20question%2C%20which%20meant%20one%20of%20us%20would%20have%20to%20quit%20our%20job%20to%20be%20a%20stay-at-home%20parent.%20Was%20the%20proximity%20worth%20it%2C%20and%20was%20the%20stress%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20the%20biggest%20question%20of%20all%3A%20When%20we%20thought%20about%20raising%20our%20family%2C%20what%20image%20came%20to%20mind%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThen%2C%20when%20we%20broke%20the%20news%20about%20my%20pregnancy%20to%20our%20respective%20parents%2C%20their%20unbridled%20joy%20confirmed%20what%20we%20had%20already%20been%20feeling.%20We%20wanted%20to%20raise%20our%20baby%20surrounded%20by%20that%20joy.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2270397144-4f41-4d7d-90df-00c63401bc78%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EStaying%20in%20Denver%20was%20the%20right%20move%20for%20us%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20we%20signed%20an%2018-month%20lease%20for%20an%20apartment%20in%20Denver.%20The%20cost%20of%20living%20was%20still%20high%2C%20and%20both%20of%20our%20careers%20remained%20unpredictable.%20But%20we%20had%20something%20invaluable%3A%20support.%20Two%20sets%20of%20grandparents%2C%20both%20within%20driving%20distance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20our%20son%20was%20born%2C%20they%20showed%20up%20with%20enchiladas%20and%20apple%20pie%2C%20with%20confident%20arms%20willing%20to%20rock%20the%20baby%20to%20sleep%20at%20four%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20with%20the%20tender%20blessings%20of%20someone%20we%20wholly%20trusted%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BGo%20lie%20down%2C%20I've%20got%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20were%20days%20I%20worried%20we'd%20taken%20a%20step%20back%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-found-suburban-life-miserable-never-moving-back-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enot%20returning%20to%20LA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20That%20we%20were%20pressing%20pause%20on%20our%20careers%2C%20especially%20for%20me%20as%20a%20screenwriter%2C%20with%20the%20industry%20so%20concentrated%20in%20California.%20But%20as%20the%20newborn%20haze%20began%20to%20lift%2C%20I%20started%20to%20see%20it%20differently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20many%20creative%20fields%2C%20especially%20as%20a%20freelancer%2C%20there's%20no%20HR%20department%2C%20no%20paid%20parental%20leave%2C%20no%20road%20map.%20A%20startup%20doesn't%20offer%20much%20certainty%2C%20either.%20What%20we%20needed%20%E2%80%94%20more%20than%20a%20city%2C%20more%20than%20a%20scene%20%E2%80%94%20was%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-rely-on-my-kids-boomer-grandparents-for-childcare-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esupport%20system%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20isn't%20a%20story%20of%20everything%20magically%20working%20out.%20Daycare%20in%20Denver%20can%20be%20prohibitively%20expensive%2C%20but%20we've%20figured%20out%20a%20childcare%20schedule%20that%20works%20for%20us%20and%20the%20grandparents%20so%20we%20can%20do%20our%20jobs.%20Work%20opportunities%20ebb%20and%20flow%2C%20and%20the%20hustle%20is%20much%20harder%20all%20these%20miles%20away.%20And%20truthfully%2C%20I%20miss%20the%20momentum%20of%20LA%20%E2%80%94%20the%20energy%2C%20the%20industry%2C%20the%20hunger.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20then%20I%20step%20outside%20and%20gaze%20in%20wonder%20at%20the%20mountains%20on%20the%20horizon.%20I%20see%20my%20baby's%20tiny%20hand%20wrapped%20around%20my%20dad's%20finger%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20it%20in%20my%20chest%3A%20this%20is%20the%20life%20we%20couldn't%20afford%20in%20LA%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20financially%20but%20emotionally.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20get%20to%20raise%20our%20child%20knowing%20he%20will%20have%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-moved-near-kids-grandparents-parenting-support-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclose%20relationship%20with%20his%20grandparents%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20We're%20not%20stretched%20to%20the%20point%20of%20breaking.%20We%20haven't%20had%20to%20choose%20between%20our%20work%20and%20our%20child.%20We%20get%20to%20be%20present.%20That%20kind%20of%20presence%20%E2%80%94%20that%20kind%20of%20joy%20%E2%80%94%20is%20worth%20everything.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-la-colorado-pregnant-family-support-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748161021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682c82c568a292900801c61f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-la-colorado-pregnant-family-support-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20husband%20and%20I%20thought%20our%20move%20from%20LA%20to%20Colorado%20would%20be%20temporary.%20When%20I%20got%20pregnant%20with%20our%20son%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20stay%20near%20our%20parents.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Emma%20Needell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-la-colorado-pregnant-family-support-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fire%20cuts%20power%20to%2045%2C000%20in%20French%20Riviera%2C%20sabotage%20suspected%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1748161018000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121391531%2Cimgsize-12964.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Ffire-cuts-power-to-45000-in-french-riviera-sabotage-suspected%2Farticleshow%2F121391359.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%2