A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse-2-1747926728-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-437095%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Black%20Box%20is%20a%20unique%2C%20multifunctional%20space%20that%20presents%20screenings%2C%20conversations%2C%20performances%2C%20presentations%2C%20workshops%2C%20and%20courses%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20G5A%20stands%20against%20the%20cityline%20as%20a%20pi%C3%A8ce%20de%20r%C3%A9sistance%20for%20the%20contemporary%20arts%2C%20daring%20urbanity%20to%20challenge%20its%20ideals.%20Through%20its%20repertoire%20of%20screenings%2C%20conversations%20and%20theatre%20festivals%2C%20it%20is%20furthering%20the%20legacy%20of%20the%20artistic%20movement%20that%20enveloped%20Mumbai%20in%20a%20tight%20embrace%20from%20the%201960s%20through%20the%201980s.%20To%20Parikh%2C%20the%20Black%20Box%20is%20a%20metaphor%20for%20potential%2C%20for%20infinite%20possibility.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20black%20void%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20any%20specific%20form%2C%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20see%20boundaries.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%20the%20conundrum%20of%20finding%20a%20middle%20ground%20between%20wanting%20to%20redesign%20completely%20and%20wanting%20to%20preserve%20the%20antiquity%20of%20the%20warehouse.%20Finally%2C%20her%20design%20philosophy%20leaned%20towards%20the%20latter.%20But%20the%20premise%20was%20always%20inclusion.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20want%20this%20to%20become%20just%20a%20venue%2C%20but%20instead%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F366709%2Fkamal-malik-ballard-estate-ambico-ice-factory-restoration-if-be-cultural-centre%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espace%20that%20would%20be%20accessible%20for%20local%20communities%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Our%20tagline%20%E2%80%98culture%2C%20community%2C%20and%20city%E2%80%99%20gives%20an%20essence%20of%20what%20G5A%20was%20meant%20to%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhere%20art%20and%20community%20convene%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReserved%20for%20VIPs%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20words%20are%20sometimes%20plastered%20on%20the%20front-row%20seats%20at%20programmes%20at%20G5A.%20Guests%20filing%20in%20leave%20the%20seats%20vacant%2C%20which%20soon%20seat%20their%20lawful%20occupants%20%E2%80%94%20the%20millworkers%2C%20the%20Kolis%2C%20members%20of%20the%20Worli%20Koliwada%20sea-faring%20community%2C%20and%20others%20in%20the%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20these%20programmes%2C%20they%20are%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmissing%20VIPs%E2%80%9D%2C%20Parikh%20points%20out.%20This%20thought%20aligns%20with%20her%20intent%20of%20making%20the%20local%20communities%20important%20stakeholders%20of%20the%20G5A%20mission.%20%E2%80%9CArt%20enables%20us%20to%20think%20differently%2C%20shifts%20something%20in%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20emphasises.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20empowers%20us%20to%20redefine%20how%20we%20live%20our%20lives%2C%20how%20we%20vote%20(from%20Leonard%20Bernstein%E2%80%99s%20quote%20that%20is%20mounted%20on%20one%20of%20their%20walls)%2C%20and%20gives%20us%20a%20kit%20for%20life.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParikh%E2%80%99s%20familiarity%20with%20contemporary%20art%20disciplines%20borrows%20from%20her%20parents.%20Her%20mother%2C%20Shaila%20Mohile%20Parikh%2C%20founded%20the%20famed%20Mohile%20Parikh%20Centre%20%E2%80%94%20an%20internationally%20renowned%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F300577%2Fbest-folk-artists-and-artisans-take-masterclasses-on-first-culture-tech-platform-memeraki%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstitution%20devoted%20to%20art%20and%20culture%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20at%20the%20NCPA%20(National%20Centre%20for%20the%20Performing%20Arts)%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20while%20her%20father%2C%20Jagdish%20Parikh%2C%20was%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Film%20Finance%20Corporation%20(%E2%80%9Cwhich%20he%20redefined%20as%20the%20National%20Film%20Development%20Corporation%E2%80%9D).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParikh%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20and%20youth%20were%20filled%20with%20encounters%20with%20the%20likes%20of%20Shyam%20Benegal%20(also%20known%20as%20the%20pioneer%20of%20parallel%20Indian%20cinema)%20Mani%20Kaul%2C%20Kumar%20Shahani%2C%20renowned%20artists%20M%20F%20Husain%2C%20Akbar%20Padamsee%2C%20Nalini%20Malani%2C%20Raza%2C%20famed%20classical%20musicians%20Vilayat%20Khan%2C%20Bhimsain%20Joshi%2C%20Shobha%20Gurtu%2C%20and%20visionary%20architects%20Charles%20Correa%20and%20B%20V%20Doshi.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20privileged%20to%20grow%20up%20in%20that%20environment%2C%20with%20all%20of%20these%20artists%20as%20a%20kind%20of%20extended%20family%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parikh%20points%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20deep%20respect%20for%20art%20was%20part%20of%20the%20family%E2%80%99s%20lingua%20franca.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22G5A%20was%20repurposed%20from%20a%20space%20that%20served%20as%20a%20warehouse%20for%20mill%20workers%20to%20now%20a%20thriving%20space%20for%20culture%20and%20arts%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-800x600.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-200x150.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FWhat-will-become-PORT-Kitchen-and-Bar_11zon-1747926447-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-437087%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22768%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D