0city%E2%80%99s%20imaginative%20palette%20once%20again%2C%20before%20contemporary%20art%20became%20an%20enigma%2C%20Parikh%20says%20she%20needed%20a%20space%20to%20let%20her%20plans%20unfold.%20The%20dots%20connected%20and%20led%20her%20to%20the%20warehouse%2C%20which%20stood%20desolate%20on%20the%20piece%20of%20land%20where%20her%20father%20earlier%20ran%20his%20printing%20press.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20first%20thought%20was%20to%20create%20a%20space%20whose%20doors%20would%20be%20open%20to%20everyone.%20A%20space%20that%20would%20feel%20welcoming%20and%20like%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20Parikh%20shares.%20Her%20intent%20was%20for%20art%20%E2%80%93%20the%20kind%20she%20had%20grown%20up%20respecting%20and%20admiring%20%E2%80%94%20to%20find%20its%20way%20once%20more%20into%20the%20city%E2%80%99s%20lexicon.%20And%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20G5A%20was%20born%2C%20marking%20out%20a%20space%20where%20art%20gets%20its%20dues.%20Parikh%20retained%20the%20warehouse%E2%80%99s%20number%20for%20its%20name%20%E2%80%94%20G5A%20as%20an%20ode%20to%20its%20legacy.%20This%20deeply%20moved%20the%20late%20Datta%20Iswalkar%20(erstwhile%20union%20leader%20of%20the%20millworkers)%20on%20his%20last%20visit%20to%20the%20warehouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Fg5a-warehouse--1747926541.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Through%20G5A%2C%20Anuradha%20Parikh%20wanted%20to%20create%20a%20space%20that%20would%20be%20accessible%20for%20local%20communities%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.co